name: unbilledPOCUPRSimple

testSteps.description: Given that I'm logged into 'Unbilled PO Receipt' page

children.description: When i open page from sidebar menu: {Accounts Payable,Unbilled PO Receipts,Close Unbilled PO Receipt}

testSteps.description: Then the 'Unbilled PO Receipts' page and its contents should show up
Then the 'Open Invoices' search result should show up
When I select first open invoices row
When I click 'Select CUPR Account' button
Then the 'Select CUPR Account' modal should show up
When I click first CUPR Account from modal
Then the 'CUPR Payment Successfully Created' modal should show up

title: Unbilled POCUPR simple
